Aloha President Kouchi, Speaker Nakamura, and Members of the Legislature:
This is to inform you that on May 29, 2026, the following bill was signed into law:
S.B. NO. 2607, S.D. 1, H.D. 1, RELATING TO LANDSCAPE ARCHITECTS.
C D. 1 ACT 064
Mahalo,
